A

AemObject - Annotation Type in io.wcm.sling.models.annotations
Injects common AEM objects that can be derived from a SlingHttpServletRequest.

I

injectionStrategy() - Method in annotation type io.wcm.sling.models.annotations.AemObject
if set to REQUIRED injection is mandatory, if set to OPTIONAL injection is optional, in case of DEFAULT the standard annotations (Optional, Required) are used.
io.wcm.sling.models.annotations - package io.wcm.sling.models.annotations
Annotations for sling model extensions.

N

O

Deprecated.
Use injectionStrategy() instead
